Text: LOL, thanks for all your efforts...  Do you have alternate site to download your stuff?  Verizon DSL blocks piratebay while TimeWarner cable got this...  http://img709.imageshack.us/img709/2063/attachwhat.jpg

Do you use IE? I use Mozilla with AdBlock Plus addon. I used to have problems with TPB using IE, but have had no issues with Mozilla. You might want to try that. Also, check to make sure you're allowing TPB through your security software. I will warn you TPB does have nasties when using IE.
